    Matches EffDated entities by a set of Identity and Parent Columns. Identity Columns are used to generate a EffDatedUniqueKey to compare equality with other entities; Parent columns are evaluated for logical match if their type implements LogicalMatcher, and basic equality if not. In addition, implements EffDatedLogicalMatcher which allows for finding all matches within a given PolicyPeriod.
